title: Farid Bouzidi
text:
Farid Bouzidi (born April 11, 1990 in <a href="Boumerd%C3%A8s">Boumerdès</a>) is an Algerian <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player who plays for <a href="RC%20Kouba">RC Kouba</a> in the <a href="Algerian%20Ligue%20Professionnelle%202">Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 2</a>.
Club career.
On May 28, 2011, Bouzidi made his professional debut for MC Alger in a league match against <a href="USM%20Annaba">USM Annaba</a>.
